  "texts": [
    "In addition, Xiong et al. [138] used the CRB rate region to illustrate the fundamental sensing and communication tradeoff for a point-to-point ISAC system under Gaussian channels, revealing the subspace tradeoff and the deterministic-random tradeoff.",
    "The tradeoff between detection probability and achievable rate was investigated by An et al. [139], demonstrating the superiority of ISAC over the radar and coexistence counterpart.",
    "ApplicationsThanks to its high spectrum efficiency, low power consumption, and small hardware size, ISAC is becoming an effective enabler for the emerging application scenarios of future 6G.",
    "In addition, the typical applications of ISAC can be summarized as below.",
    "V2XIt is expected that V2X networks can simultaneously achieve high-resolution positioning and high-speed information transmission to enable the autonomous driving [22,23]."
  ]
}